The paper discusses query optimization, which is a core topic in database systems (cs.DB). The use of sampling and probabilistic methods also suggests a connection to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The iterative algorithm and complexity analysis are related to data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
